author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Nemex updates on construction of 1,000 photovoltaic power plants
text:
Oct 21 Nemex SA :
* Said on Tuesday that the agreement for cooperation on construction of 1,000 photovoltaic power plants was signed with Siec Parkow Energii Slonecznej Sp. z o.o.
* The company informed on deal on June 26 [ID: nFWN0ZB072]
